{
  "info": {
    "name": "Smart Delivery - Route Service",
    "description": "# Route Service\n\nManages delivery routes and driver assignments for the Smart Delivery System.\n\n## Features\n- Create, Read, Update, Delete routes\n- Assign/Unassign drivers to routes\n- Filter routes by status\n- Get driver's assigned routes\n\n## Route Statuses\n| Status | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `active` | Route is currently active |\n| `completed` | Route has been completed |\n| `cancelled` | Route was cancelled |\n\n## Authorization\n| Endpoint | Admin | Manager | Driver |\n|----------|-------|---------|--------|\n| Create Route | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| Get All Routes | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| Get My Routes | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| Update Route | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| Assign Driver | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| Delete Route | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n\n## Base URL\n- Direct: `http://localhost:3002`\n- Via Gateway: `http://localhost:3000/api/routes`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
